25 Jun 2015
-----------

0. How to use this common utility in a project
   In that project's Build Path -> Configure Build Path... -> Projects Tab -> Add
   
1. Finally decided to create a utility package. Common ones are:
   . network
   . data parsing
   
   commonly used external libraries are:
   . Google GSON (gson-2.3.1) or Jackson
   . Jsoup (jsoup-1.8.2)
   . Apache commons
   . Joda Time
   . Language detection (langdetect and jsonic-1.2.0)
   . String similarity
   . Proxy detector (js.jar and proxy-vole_20131209)
   . rome-1.5, rome-modules-1.5, room-utils-1.5 (requires jdom-2, slf4j-api) http://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.rometools 


